sequenceDiagram
    participant USER as User Request
    participant SVC_A as Service A\n(payments-api)
    participant SVC_B as Service B\n(fraud-detection)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    participant LOKI as Grafana Loki\n(logs)
    participant TEMPO as Grafana Tempo\n(traces)
    participant MIMIR as Grafana Mimir\n(metrics)
    participant GRAFANA as Grafana\n(correlation UI)

    Note over USER,GRAFANA: Normal request — all signals correlated

    USER->>SVC_A: POST /payments\nHeaders: traceparent: 00-TRACE_ID-SPAN_A-01

    SVC_A->>SVC_A: Emit structured log:\n{level:info, trace_id:TRACE_ID,\nspan_id:SPAN_A, msg:"payment received",\namount:99.99}
    SVC_A->>LOKI: Log line (with trace_id)

    SVC_A->>SVC_B: GET /fraud-check\nHeaders: traceparent: 00-TRACE_ID-SPAN_B-01
    SVC_B->>SVC_B: Emit log:\n{level:info, trace_id:TRACE_ID,\nspan_id:SPAN_B, msg:"fraud score: 0.02"}
    SVC_B->>LOKI: Log line (with trace_id)

    SVC_A->>DB: SELECT * FROM accounts WHERE id=?
    DB-->>SVC_A: Row returned (45ms)
    SVC_A->>SVC_A: Emit trace span:\n{trace_id, span_id, db.query,\ndb.statement, duration_ms: 45}

    SVC_A->>TEMPO: Full trace (TRACE_ID)\nAll spans: A→B→DB

    SVC_A->>MIMIR: Increment metric:\nhttp_requests_total{service="payments",status="200"}\npayment_processing_duration_seconds histogram

    SVC_A-->>USER: 200 OK

    Note over USER,GRAFANA: Alert fires — engineer investigates

    MIMIR->>GRAFANA: Alert: payment_error_rate > 1%\nAnnotation: trace_id=TRACE_ID_ERR

    GRAFANA->>MIMIR: Query metrics: show error spike
    GRAFANA->>LOKI: Query logs:\n{service="payments"} |= "trace_id=TRACE_ID_ERR"
    LOKI-->>GRAFANA: Log lines with trace_id
    GRAFANA->>TEMPO: Fetch trace: TRACE_ID_ERR
    TEMPO-->>GRAFANA: Full trace — shows\nfraud-detection timeout\nat span B (3001ms)

    Note over GRAFANA,GRAFANA: Engineer sees in one UI:\n1. Metric spike (Mimir)\n2. Log lines with error details (Loki)\n3. Exact trace showing fraud-detection timeout (Tempo)\nRoot cause identified in < 2 minutes
